Issue 1: Stat-editing inconsistency (Value Mismatch/Reset)
Context: When setting base stats or current stats to values exceeding standard game limits, the in-game party screen reflects an inconsistent number.
In some cases, the value does not match the input.
In other cases, the value matches initially but reverts or "sanitizes" back to a lower number after a period.
Condition: Investigating. (Note: Initial bug report was logged during late-night testing; currently re-verifying to rule out user error.)
